events.name: Duke Blue Devils at Louisville Cardinals

headlines.description: Lamar Jackson provided a cushion with a 2-yard touchdown run with 1:32 remaining and No. 7 Louisville held off Duke 24-14 on Friday night.

video.headline: Jackson, Louisville keeps Duke winless in ACC

events.name: Memphis Tigers at Tulane Green Wave

headlines.description: Darrell Henderson had two long touchdowns, one rushing and one receiving, to lead Memphis to a 24-14 victory over Tulane on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Henderson TDs lead Memphis past Tulane 24-14.

video.headline: Memphis takes screen pass 46 yards to the house

events.name: San Diego State Aztecs at Fresno State Bulldogs

headlines.description: Donnel Pumphrey rushed for 220 yards and two touchdowns, surpassing 1,000 yards for the season and moving into the NCAA top 10 for his career, in San Diego State's 17-3 win Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: SDSU's Pumphrey rushes into NCAA top 10 in win

events.name: Mississippi State Bulldogs at BYU Cougars

headlines.description: The criticisms of Taysom Hill ran deep in 2016 as the dual-threat quarterback just hasn't quite looked like the same dynamic player that was a Heisman candidate 2013. Season-ending injuries in 20
headlines.shortLinkText: Hill scores 4 TDs, BYU beats Mississippi State 28-21

video.headline: BYU holds off Mississippi State's last gasp OT chance
